{"tid":2329423,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜CD Projekt Red.....(認真)","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T10:26:52.000Z","uid":67454,"like":8,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f260c490a3917df0976d276e06e94f1f0ade8ae9","tid":2329423,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"細個開始打機果陣好拎憎game廠，覺得Level5、Konami、EA好拎茅（當年EA收購westwood），次次出game都好似教科書一樣既冷飯好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地收哂皮，先知果D老練既創意／技術係好野黎<br />\n<br />\n洛克人既玩法、莎木（全盛時期）既地圖、Dark Souls對難度既執著，都係到唔再出／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多人都反CDPR，但係老實講佢既欺騙技術、奶共能力、對bug既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家2077&gt;&gt;No man sky）<br />\n<br />\n我諗CDPR最多都係做多1、2年就收皮，其實玩得1日得1日，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：Atari迷"},{"pid":"de166b8eb2b24863ee8fc24a045a787b13af81b1","tid":2329423,"uid":252784,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"真心覺得CDPR唔應該做game 應該玩政治 <br />\n佢嗰啲個人崇拜 虛假宣傳 奶共打壓 拉一派打一派手法真心厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb00f14563fd7ac95c57243b405143516f97b1d","tid":2329423,"uid":64522,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de166b8eb2b24863ee8fc24a045a787b13af81b1","tid":2329423,"uid":252784,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"真心覺得CDPR唔應該做game 應該玩政治 <br />\n佢嗰啲個人崇拜 虛假宣傳 奶共打壓 拉一派打一派手法真心厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"叻撚過共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387921e7c223188384e76f25888c78ab433f9b26","tid":2329423,"uid":48759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"CDPR應該收皮<br />\n轉行去寫小說"},{"pid":"3c8dc9179fe9fc798b80f1ff8b9b3cd8cdd1ed17","tid":2329423,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387921e7c223188384e76f25888c78ab433f9b26","tid":2329423,"uid":48759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT